alphabetsoup.waypointgraph
Class Waypoint

java.lang.Object
  alphabetsoup.framework.Circle
      alphabetsoup.waypointgraph.Waypoint

public class Waypoint
extends Circle

Waypoint represents a location and any objects that are relevant to that location, such as Buckets, Bucket storage locations, WordStations, and LetterStations. Waypoints connect to each other to make up a graph of paths for Bucketbots to traverse.

Author:
Chris Hazard
